tem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532791\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532791\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104upd1665702601935.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/upd1665702601935.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/upd1665702601935.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"upd1665702601935\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $keytype\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"upd1665702601935___keytype_272042\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the type of the specified key.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"upd1665702601935__topic_d85295e1_d85296e1_d85297e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"upd1665702601935__p_d85298e1_d85299e1_d85300e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keytype</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"upd1665702601935__section_w201ab1b7b5_w202ab1b7_w203ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"upd1665702601935__p_d85301e1_d85302e1_d85303e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">if ($keytype(\"CUSTOMER\", 2) != \"I\")</code> ...</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"upd1665702601935__topic_d56632e1_d56633e1_d56634e1_d56635e1_d56636e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d724759e91\">\n                       Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"upd1665702601935__d6103e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"upd1665702601935__d6103e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"upd1665702601935__d6103e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"upd1665702601935__d6103e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__d6103e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__d6103e20__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__d6103e20__entry__3\">Entity name.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__d6103e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__d6103e20__entry__2\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__d6103e20__entry__3\"> Key identifier; the value will be\n\t\t\t\t truncated to form an integer. <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"upd1665702601935__d6103e80\">1, the primary key.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"upd1665702601935__d6103e83\">2, 3, 4, and so on, the number that\n\t\t\t\t\t\tidentifies a candidate key that has been defined for <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>. </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"upd1665702601935__topic_d56637e1_d56638e1_d56639e1_d56640e1_d56641e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d724759e172\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8957e1_d8958e1_d8959e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keytype</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8957e1_d8958e1_d8959e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8957e1_d8958e1_d8959e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8957e1_d8958e1_d8959e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"\"</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8957e1_d8958e1_d8959e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span>\n\t\tcontains the exact error.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8957e1_d8958e1_d8959e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">P</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8957e1_d8958e1_d8959e1__entry__2\">\n                        KeyNumber is a primary key (that is, KeyNumber is 1).\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8957e1_d8958e1_d8959e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">C</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8957e1_d8958e1_d8959e1__entry__2\">\n                        KeyNumber is a candidate key.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8957e1_d8958e1_d8959e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">I</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8957e1_d8958e1_d8959e1__entry__2\">\n                        KeyNumber is an index.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8960e1_d8961e1_d8962e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following this\n            Function</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8960e1_d8961e1_d8962e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8960e1_d8961e1_d8962e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Error constant</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8960e1_d8961e1_d8962e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8960e1_d8961e1_d8962e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8960e1_d8961e1_d8962e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8960e1_d8961e1_d8962e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> The entity name provided is not a valid\n\t\t\t\t name or the entity is not present in the component structure. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8960e1_d8961e1_d8962e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1104</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8960e1_d8961e1_d8962e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_KEY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"upd1665702601935__table_d8960e1_d8961e1_d8962e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> The key number provided is not valid; for\n\t\t\t\t example, the key number was out of range. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"upd1665702601935__topic_d56642e1_d56643e1_d56644e1_d56645e1_d56646e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d724759e369\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"upd1665702601935__p_d85313e1_d85314e1_d85315e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"upd1665702601935__section_ekv_fkb_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d724759e378\">Example: Defining the Validation for Specific Keys </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keytype</span> function to\n               define the validation for specific keys in the validateKey trigger. (The validateKey\n               trigger is activated only for primary and candidate keys.)</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"upd1665702601935__pre_m5h_gkb_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger validateKey\nselectcase $keytype(\"MYENTITY\", $curkey)\n case \"P\" ; perform validation for the primary key\n ...\n case \"C\" ; perform validation for all candidate keys\n ...\n elsecase ; oops\n message \"Cannot validate this key\"\n message \"Context: %%$dataerrorcontext\"\nendselectcase\nend; validateKey</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrk1665702576500.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Validate</a><p>Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwi1665702576586.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatefield</a><p>Validate a field of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1665702576817.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatekey</a><p>Validate a key of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bwv1665702576896.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validateocc</a><p>Validate an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jqe1665702576424.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$dataerrorcontext</a><p>Return the context of the last validation error.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nij1665702601782.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keymod</a><p>Return a value indicating whether the specified key has been modified.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcw1719485700746.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keyvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/epv1719810593542.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$totkeys</a><p>Return the total number of keys for an entity.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532791\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532791\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$keytype Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $keytype Return the type of the specified key. $keytype ( Entity , KeyNumber ) Example: if ($keytype(\"CUSTOMER\", 2) != \"I\") ... Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. KeyNumber Numeric Key identifier; the value will be truncated to form an integer. 1, the primary key. 2, 3, 4, and so on, the number that identifies a candidate key that has been defined for Entity . Return Values Table 2. Values returned in $keytype Value Meaning \"\" An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. P KeyNumber is a primary key (that is, KeyNumber is 1). C KeyNumber is a candidate key. I KeyNumber is an index. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following this Function Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not present in the component structure. -1104 <UPROCERR_KEY> The key number provided is not valid; for example, the key number was out of range. Use Allowed in all component types. Example: Defining the Validation for Specific Keys The following example uses the $keytype function to define the validation for specific keys in the validateKey trigger. (The validateKey trigger is activated only for primary and candidate keys.) trigger validateKey selectcase $keytype(\"MYENTITY\", $curkey) case \"P\" ; perform validation for the primary key ... case \"C\" ; perform validation for all candidate keys ... elsecase ; oops message \"Cannot validate this key\" message \"Context: %%$dataerrorcontext\" endselectcase end; validateKey Copy Related Links Validate Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default). validatefield Validate a field of the current occurrence. validatekey Validate a key of the current occurrence. validateocc Validate an occurrence. $dataerrorcontext Return the context of the last validation error. $keymod Return a value indicating whether the specified key has been modified. $keyvalidation Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation. $totkeys Return the total number of keys for an entity. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}